    "directions_source_text": "Mix the yogurt, the milk, the cream, the salt, and the sugar into a bowl. Heat the bowl to 80\u00b0C while stirring. Once the temperature has been reached, add the citric acid and mix well. Heat up to 90\u00b0C, then let it cool down until it reaches room temperature. Pour the cheese into the cheesecloth and let the whey drip. Store in the fridge."
